title: Disha Patani Has Someone More Beautiful In Her Family, Who Is She?
text:
Disha Patani Has Someone More Beautiful In Her Family, Who Is She? 754 396 Meet Khushboo Patani, Disha's elder sister. Loading... 
Don't they look like identical twins? Disha has two siblings, Khushboo being the eldest. Loading... Disha and her sister Khushboo differentiate in their nature. Loading... 
Disha, on the one hand, is very bubbly and outspoken, Khushboo on the other, is introvert and prefers solace. Khushboo is closer to their mother while Disha is very closer to their dad. Loading... Khushboo too is known for her simplicity. Loading... Have a look at their family picture, with Disha's parents, elder sister and younger brother. Loading... While Disha is now a well-known actress in Bollywood, Khushboo preferred to maintain a simple life. Loading... It looks like Disha is present in this picture. But no, it's Khushboo. Loading...
